hopobject.body: How long have you lived here? rxnoprescriptionbuyonlinerx.com The English, a phlegmatic bunch, did not come out on the streets in protest. Nor have they objected much in the past when Labour has used Westminster MPs from its Scottish and Welsh heartlands to foist its policies on unwilling English MPs, as it did with tuition fees and foundation hospitals. The fact that Scottish MPs at Westminster have no say over higher education or health in Scotland makes the system even barmier.
